<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 01:00:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>降息希望支撑亚洲股市和黄金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-19/</link><description>由于预期美国经济将避免衰退且通胀降温将启动降息周期，全球股市创下九个月来最好的一周，亚洲股市周一稍事休息。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 00:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾船只在南海“故意相撞”中国船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-deliberately-collided-with-chinese-vessel-south-2024-08-19/</link><description>中国海警周一发表声明称，一艘菲律宾船只无视其多次警告，在有争议的南海以“不专业且危险”的方式“故意相撞”中国船只。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 00:17:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-vessel-deliberately-collided-with-chinese-vessel-south-2024-08-19/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国软着陆希望提振新兴市场资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-18/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 21:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-18/</guid></item><item><title>越南最高领导人苏林抵达中国会见习近平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-top-leader-lam-arrives-china-set-meet-xi-jinping-2024-08-18/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，越南最高领导人苏林周日抵达中国进行为期三天的访问，北京外交部表示，访问期间将包括与国家主席习近平和国务院总理李强的会面。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 03:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-top-leader-lam-arrives-china-set-meet-xi-jinping-2024-08-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国在暂停后发布新的黄金进口配额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-issues-new-gold-import-quotas-after-pause-sources-2024-08-16/</link><description>四位知情人士告诉路透社，尽管金价创历史新高，但中国几家银行已获得央行新的黄金进口配额，预计需求将会复苏。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-issues-new-gold-import-quotas-after-pause-sources-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>李克强：中国将着力促进消费提振经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-focus-boosting-consumption-improve-economy-premier-says-2024-08-16/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国总理李强周五在内阁全体会议上表示，必须大力提振经济，国家将把重点放在刺激消费上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 11:45:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-focus-boosting-consumption-improve-economy-premier-says-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟高额关税影响中国生物柴油生产商寻求新出路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-biodiesel-producers-seek-new-outlets-hefty-eu-tariffs-bite-2024-08-16/</link><description>生物燃料高管和分析师表示，中国生物柴油生产商正在亚洲寻找新的出口渠道，并探索生产其他生物燃料，因为其最大买家欧盟的供应在反倾销关税之前枯竭。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 11:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-biodiesel-producers-seek-new-outlets-hefty-eu-tariffs-bite-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>讲解员：什么是锑？中国为何限制锑出口？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/what-is-antimony-why-is-china-curbing-its-exports-2024-08-16/</link><description>中国周四表示，以国家安全为由，将从 9 月 15 日起对部分锑产品实施出口管制，这是北京自去年以来实施的限制战略矿产出口措施的又一举措。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 11:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/what-is-antimony-why-is-china-curbing-its-exports-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>伦敦证券交易所数据显示，7月份中国和沙特阿拉伯是俄罗斯燃料油的最大买家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-saudi-arabia-top-buyers-russian-fuel-oil-july-lseg-data-shows-2024-08-16/</link><description>交易商表示，伦敦证券交易所周五公布的数据显示，中国和沙特阿拉伯是俄罗斯 7 月份海运燃料油和减压柴油 (VGO) 出口的最大目的地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 10:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-saudi-arabia-top-buyers-russian-fuel-oil-july-lseg-data-shows-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>恒大境内子公司管理人在会议前向债权人寻求详细信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/evergrande-onshore-units-administrator-seeks-details-creditors-ahead-meeting-2024-08-16/</link><description>官方文件显示，恒大在岸主要子公司的管理人已要求债权人在 11 月 14 日举行的第一次债权人会议之前提供这家陷入困境的房地产开发商所欠债务的详细信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 10:13:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/evergrande-onshore-units-administrator-seeks-details-creditors-ahead-meeting-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称美国导弹系统对中国不构成威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/international-ties-boost-philippines-security-economy-foreign-minister-says-2024-08-16/</link><description>菲律宾周五试图向中国保证，美国中程导弹系统在其领土上的存在不会对中国构成威胁，也不会破坏该地区的稳定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 08:50:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/international-ties-boost-philippines-security-economy-foreign-minister-says-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国暂时阻止了债券多头的脚步</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-manages-halt-bond-bulls-their-tracks-now-2024-08-16/</link><description>中国债券长期疯狂的涨势已陷入停滞，随着北京方面加大干预力度阻止收益率下跌，投资者纷纷退出，价格下跌，成交量大幅下滑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 08:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-manages-halt-bond-bulls-their-tracks-now-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国AMEC因“军事公司”标签起诉美国国防部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-amec-sues-us-defence-department-over-military-company-label-2024-08-16/</link><description>中国领先的芯片设备制造商之一先进微制造设备公司（AMEC）周五表示，已对美国国防部提起联邦诉讼，质疑其被指定为“中国军事公司”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 07:34:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-amec-sues-us-defence-department-over-military-company-label-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国步履蹒跚的经济增长重振了现金券的讨论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-faltering-growth-revives-cash-vouchers-talk-2024-08-16/</link><description>中国又一轮糟糕的经济数据给北京带来了压力，要求其进一步放松财政宽松，甚至发放购物券，以使经济增长回到今年约5%的目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 06:22:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-faltering-growth-revives-cash-vouchers-talk-2024-08-16/</guid></item><item><title>高层领导人会晤时，中国和越南着眼于加强铁路建设</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/rail-links-high-agenda-china-vietnam-leaders-meeting-2024-08-16/</link><description>官员们表示，随着越南邻国寻求促进贸易，越南新任命的领导人苏林下周将前往中国会见中国国家主席习近平，铁路建设将成为重要议题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 05:25:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/rail-links-high-agenda-china-vietnam-leaders-meeting-2024-08-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>